title: Rito Please Gib Fix
body: I logged in around 5 am and waited for a match and just before the match was about to start apparently I LEFT THE QUEUE ??? So i thought aight its cool ill wait 5 more mins for queue dodging i dont mind... so i go to the game mode selection section and only thing i can select are maps... ranked/normal/etc is gone, theres NOTHING there... i cant select ranked so when i go into matchmaking its instantly normal... Please gib fix Rito

replies.body: Ranked Q's are currently disabled for the upcoming maintenance. Always be sure to check the [**status page**](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) for info when certain Q's go down!
